research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Strawn City, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro Tem, and four Aldermen/Alderwoman. Information was gathered from the City of Strawn's official website and the Texas State Directory Online. Council positions appear to be at-large. There was a minor discrepancy in one source listing DeLane Abbott as Mayor Pro Tem, but more recent and official directories consistently list Aron Johnson in that role, with DeLane Abbott as an Alderman.
